query:
SELECT cc.componentName, cc.nominalThickness, cc.previousThickness, cc.actualThickness, cc.minimumThickness, i.vesselTagNumber 
FROM componentCalculations cc 
JOIN professionalReports pr ON cc.reportId = pr.id 
JOIN inspections i ON pr.inspectionId = i.id 
WHERE i.vesselTagNumber = '54-11-067' LIMIT 10;
